text: Haedropleura laeta is a species of sea snail, a marine gastropod mollusk in the family Horaiclavidae.* Tucker, J.K. 2004 Catalog of recent and fossil turrids (Mollusca: Gastropoda). Zootaxa 682:1–1295. ==Description== ==Distribution== This marine species occurs off Sumatra, Indonesia. ==References== * Thiele, J. (1929). Handbuch der Systematischen Weichtierkunde. Vol. 1.
